title: Ep.12: Lincoln Riley to USC, Steelers Next QB, WSU Dominance, Georgia Vs Alabama Preview, Packers, Patriots Hot Streak and More.
description: Lincoln Riley claims he is going to make USC the mecca of college football and he is more than capable. The steelers playoff hopes are very slim and its time for them to be on the QB hunt. Is this the start of Jayden De Laura and WSU dominance over UW? Packers game review, how far can the patriots take this, and more.
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
